


'''tageldunt Kirya''' s tmaziɣt ( '''ⴽⵉⵔⵢⴰ''' ) d tageldunt tamaziɣt taqbaylit ɣef ugdud n [[taddukli n 05 n yiderman]] yeddren deg tasut tis ukkuz n tlalit n sidna [[Ɛisa]] , qqaren-as daɣen Silya neɣ Sirya . 

== Tudert ==
Tlul-d deg [[Tamurt n Leqbayel|tmurt n leqbayel]] deg tlemmast n tasut tis ukkuz n tlalit ; baba-s d aɣella adunati Flabyus Nubil  id-yurwen aṭas n warrac 07 d igejdanen ( Zammak Maskuzil Mazusa Ǧildun [[Firmus]] ) d nettat i d taqcict gar-asen ; Sammak d mmi-s si baba-s kan 

== Tagrawla n firmus ==
Yemmut Nubil yeǧǧa-d s deffir-s idrimen d yigran d tgelda meqqren . D Zammak i yuɣalen d agellid imi d netta i d amenzu maca yella d taxatemt gar yiḍudan n yirumaniyen , d ayen i yesserfan gma-s Firmus , imiren i as-yekksen tagelda yerna yenɣa-t imi yettwaḥseb d axabit . Irumaniyen rfan imi yeḍra way-a sg yimiren yettili-d ccwal gar-asen d yimaziɣen , armi wwḍen ɣer tegrawla s ddaw n tmehla n Firmus i yseddan yid-s atmaten-is-nniḍen , kirya tedda d gma-s di tneglufin tella tettɛawan wid ijerḥen , tbennu tizeɣwa n useǧǧi deg wussan n talwit tettara ɣer yiderman akken ad tent-sillez ad ddun d  gma-s . Tkemmel kan akken . 

Ardekal n tezɣent Firmus / Ǧildun 

Yeffeɣ Ǧildun i tegrawla n gma-s , yeffeɣ seg  tdunatit xedmen-as [[abellez]] akken ad yekcem takatulikit , yerna ɣer yiserdasen irumaniyen yexdem-d tazɣent ( la crise ) akked gma-s . Nnan-d kra belli Kirya tuɣal tettazal gar lmur d Yirumaniyen akken ad d-awi talwit kra nnan-d tedda d Firmus d tegrawla-s tessulez kra n yiderman ad dduklen yid-s , maca xesren , teɣli teddukla-nni ma d Firmus yenɣa iman-is .

